{"tid":1579381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果決意去沙田既手足，只係希望你地記得一句","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T07:00:41.000Z","uid":57012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b60dacd3b54be93bda6a2038baf8979f10987785","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"睇到好多post 都係話去沙田同唔好去沙田<br />\n<br />\n只係想講，如果各位手足或者街坊都好<br />\n<br />\n要去既希望你地記得一句説話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要打波有無人跟隊</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pU1EVUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpU1EVUs.jpg&h=2df7287c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"093451abdfb6a65c8f5ccf58966ca9da9b02bc0e","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有無人跟隊</span></span>"},{"pid":"637895c470b8d5403ac7a79b4d39afb3a994bf32","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"21bc3a8e17af1cc80159332540d9fa84ab89d664","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"98c9de570d9a2d2097c1e52336d6af8fd6d16c34","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"74725d74e9fc6b85f37da183ecc77705a360b488","tid":1579381,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"558cdcd892d815f362e5e6518e7fdcca8e3583d2","tid":1579381,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc